07:38.911 --> 07:39.912
Oh, Jesus.

07:39.996 --> 07:42.290
<i>Besides, the show could use
a little narrative shift.</i>

07:42.623 --> 07:45.710
Let's do this. These orders are coming
straight from the fucking Death Star.

07:45.793 --> 07:49.130
Chip, I'm not...
I'm not covering a fucking fire, okay?

07:49.213 --> 07:52.425
Just send Bradley.
Get her off my ass for a few days.

07:52.508 --> 07:54.886
