left me to host your fucking fund-raiser.

08:14.530 --> 08:16.866
Okay. Look, I-I... I was upset...

08:16.949 --> 08:21.746
Yes, but you're always upset or stressed,
and I just cannot take it anymore. Okay?

08:23.706 --> 08:24.916
I love our daughter.

08:24.999 --> 08:29.420
But years of having a relationship
with a charming narcissist

08:29.503 --> 08:31.339
is fucking killing me.

08:32.673 --> 08:34.383
You're not in love with me.

08:35.218 --> 08:37.762
And I am not in love with you anymore.

08:43.476 --> 08:44.477
And?

08:45.937 --> 08:47.396
I want a divorce.

08:56.697 --> 08:58.574
Well, no.

08:59.742 --> 09:01.994
It's not entirely up to you,
believe it or not.

09:02.078 --> 09:04.705
Jason, this... this is why
we are separated. Because...

09:04.789 --> 09:06.350
Listen.
We don't have to do the family calendars.

09:06.374 --> 09:08.626
You don't have to host my fund-raisers
with me anymore.

09:08.709 --> 09:13.464
No, Alex. We separated because
we argue constantly just like this.

09:13.547 --> 09:14.549
Yes, we do.

09:14.632 --> 09:18.678
And because, deep down, I am furious
with you for never putting me first,

09:18.761 --> 09:22.890
and you are furious with me
because I am angry about it,

09:22.974 --> 09:25.726
and because you believe
you have a God-given right

09:25.810 --> 09:28.437
