I will never speak to you again...

09:36.153 --> 09:37.196
ever.

09:37.780 --> 09:39.198
Fine. Fine.

09:41.909 --> 09:44.787
Okay, um, look.

09:45.538 --> 09:47.081
We can't get a divorce.

09:48.916 --> 09:51.460
- I'm already on thin ice with America.
- Oh, God.

09:51.544 --> 09:54.380
A divorce will just...
put me over the edge. And I can...

09:54.463 --> 09:57.466
This is happening, Alex.

09:58.301 --> 10:01.262
