10:34.837 --> 10:36.756
Beca... Because, because...

10:38.507 --> 10:40.176
I have to go to California today.

10:42.511 --> 10:45.514
We're covering the fires.
That's why Chip has been calling me.

10:45.598 --> 10:46.599
Alex.

10:46.682 --> 10:49.810
