11:25.805 --> 11:30.101
Hey, so sorry. I was sound... sound asleep.

11:30.184 --> 11:32.186
Um, you're right.

11:32.270 --> 11:34.981
<i>It... It's important.
Of course, I'll be there.</i>

11:35.064 --> 11:37.358
Fantastic. Thank you.
Plane can leave at 11:00.

11:37.733 --> 11:41.112
Okay, I'll see you then.
Oh, eh, um, don't bring Bradley.

11:41.946 --> 11:45.449
You just fucking told me to bring...
You know what? It doesn't matter.

11:45.992 --> 11:48.303
She's already going.
Fred wants her there. You're both going.

11:48.327 --> 11:51.372
It's gonna be a ratings bonanza.
Pack your stuff. Car's coming in an hour.

11:51.455 --> 11:52.748
Oh, fuck, fine!

12:36.792 --> 12:38.628
All right, I'm here. Let's go.

13:11.452 --> 13:12.745
Copy just came in.

13:12.828 --> 13:14.330
Oh, thank you.

13:16.249 --> 13:18.209
I'm glad we're getting out of town
for a few days.

13:18.292 --> 13:22.380
Yeah, we could definitely all use a change
of scenery, even if it's a deadly fire.

13:22.463 --> 13:24.090
