13:39.814 --> 13:41.534
Oh, wow. Nah, I'm just playing.
You're fine.

13:41.732 --> 13:44.318
Look, the staff, they barely know you.
It's only been a week.

13:44.402 --> 13:47.154
Give them some time. Okay?
You're pretty likable.

13:48.739 --> 13:49.824
Thanks.

13:49.907 --> 13:51.617
I need some coffee. You want some?

13:51.701 --> 13:53.202
- Nah, I'm all good.
- Okay.

14:04.130 --> 14:05.548
It's the travel booker.

14:05.631 --> 14:06.632
What?

14:06.716 --> 14:10.553
