because of the mandatory evacuations.

14:10.636 --> 14:13.598
And the only one that's available
doesn't have any suites.

14:14.390 --> 14:17.685
Well, can't they kick out
some of the displaced families?

14:18.895 --> 14:20.354
I do need room for my diamonds.

14:20.438 --> 14:22.315
- So that's a "yes." Got it.
- Jesus.

14:23.316 --> 14:25.276
Who's telling people
that I need all these things?

14:25.943 --> 14:26.944
Hmm?

14:27.528 --> 14:30.239
This is why celebrities
get really crappy reputations.

14:31.407 --> 14:33.492
And by being difficult to work with.

14:35.411 --> 14:37.705
It's been two days
since the Ashley Brown interview.

14:37.788 --> 14:38.998
What's your point?

14:39.498 --> 14:42.144
What are we doing? You're gonna
have to talk to Bradley at some point.

14:42.168 --> 14:44.128
Or... Or make some eye contact.

14:44.211 --> 14:48.174
Chip, I don't give a fuck.
Just leave me alone on it, all right?

14:48.716 --> 14:51.177
I have this other natural disaster
I have to deal with.

14:51.260 --> 14:53.763
Okay. I'm sorry. I'm just...

14:57.600 --> 14:59.852
<i>All right, folks,
we have just about another hour to go</i>

14:59.936 --> 15:01.604
<i>before we touch down in Burbank.</i>

15:01.687 --> 15:04.607
<i>I hope you guys
are having a good time back there.</i>

15:04.690 --> 15:06.359
<i>It's been a pleasure serving you.</i>

15:22.875 --> 15:24.252
Mommy!

15:47.066 --> 15:49.443
Let's go, come on. Hold my hand.
Don't let go.

15:57.118 --> 15:59.120
Water... Here if you need 'em.

16:01.789 --> 16:02.832
Sorry this took so long.

16:02.915 --> 16:03.916
Jesus.

16:04.000 --> 16:06.002
Any port in a storm, huh?

16:06.085 --> 16:07.461
You sure about that?

